summary: This is an FBI FD-302 form documenting a proffer interview conducted on August 19, 2019, at the Southern District of New York. The interview was conducted pursuant to a proffer agreement with a Bureau of Prisons (BOP) registrant (number 79427-054) to gather information relating to an investigation. The document notes the presence of an AUSA and multiple special agents.

keyFacts: A proffer interview was conducted on August 19, 2019, with a BOP registrant (number 79427-054) as part of an investigation.
The interview took place at the Southern District of New York office in New York City.
Attendees included an AUSA and special agents from the FBI and the Department of Justice Office of the Inspector General.
The document is an FBI FD-302 form, which records the substance of an interview but contains no recommendations or conclusions.
The document reference number is EFTA00141115 and the case number is 90A-NY-3151227.
